<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span style="color:#008000">(٣)</span> بَابُ أَركَانِ الإِيمَانِ وَثَمَرَاتِهِ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span style="color:#006d98">س ١٤:</span> مَا أَرْكَانُ الْإِيمَانِ؟<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>أَرْكَانُ الْإِيمَانِ سِتَّةٌ،<span style="color:#006d98"> وَهِيَ:</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>١ - الْإِيمَانُ بِاللهِ تَعَالَى.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>٢ - الْإِيمَانُ بِمَلَائِكَتِهِ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>٣ - الْإِيمَانُ بِكُتُبِهِ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>٤ - الْإِيمَانُ بِرُسُلِهِ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>٥ - الْإِيمَانُ بِالْيَوْمِ الْآخِرِ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>٦ - الْإِيمَانُ بِالْقَدَرِ خَيْرِهِ وَشَرِّهِ مِنَ اللهِ تَعَالَى.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>* * *<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span style="color:#006d98">س ١٥:</span> مَا مَعْنَى الْإِيمَانِ بِاللهِ تَعَالَى؟<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span style="color:#006d98">الْإِيمَانُ بِاللهِ تَعَالَى:</span> هُوَ التَّصْدِيقُ الْجَازِمُ وَالْإِقْرَارُ الْكَامِلُ بِوُجُودِ اللهِ تَعَالَى، وَرُبُوبِيَّتِهِ، وَأُلُوهِيَّتِهِ، وَأَسْمَائِهِ وَصِفَاتِهِ.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>* * *<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>